OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,FA naval blockade has "completely
OL,7,Fhalted economic trade going into and
OL,8,Fout of Iran by sea," the US military
OL,9,Fsaid on Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe blockade of all of Iran's ports
OL,12,Fbegan on Monday afternoon, after the
OL,13,FIslamic Republic had effectively
OL,14,Fclosed the Strait of Hormuz to
OL,15,Fcommercial shipping more than a month
OL,16,Fago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
