CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776359147
OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,FThe strait is a crucial shipping
OL,7,Fchannel, through which about a fifth
OL,8,Fof the world's oil passes, giving
OL,9,FTehran a great deal of leverage in its
OL,10,Fwar with the US and Israel.
OL,12,FIn a statement, US Central Command's
OL,13,FAdmiral Brad Cooper said: "An
OL,14,Festimated 90% of Iran's economy is
OL,15,Ffueled by international trade by sea.
OL,17,F"In less than 36 hours since the
OL,18,Fblockade was implemented, US forces
OL,19,Fhave completely halted economic trade
OL,20,Fgoing into and out of Iran by sea."
OL,26,@|D@cO]
