OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump's
OL,7,Fannouncement of a blockade came after
OL,8,Fnegotiations between Iran and the US,
OL,9,Fheld in Pakistan, failed to reach a
OL,10,Fbreakthrough at the weekend.
OL,12,FHinting at further talks in Pakistan,
OL,13,FTrump told an ABC's chief Washington
OL,14,FCorrespondent Jonathan Kar that he
OL,15,Fdidn't think it would be necessary to
OL,16,Fextent a two-week ceasefire due to end
OL,17,Fon 21 April.
OL,19,F"I think you're going to be watching
OL,20,Fan amazing two days ahead," Trump said.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
