OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776359147
OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,F"It could end either way, but I think
OL,7,Fa deal is preferable because then they
OL,8,Fcan rebuild.
OL,10,F"They really do have a different
OL,11,Fregime now. No matter what, we took
OL,12,Fout the radicals."
OL,14,FMeanwhile US Vice President JD Vance
OL,15,Fsaid that Iran could "thrive" if it
OL,16,Fcommits to not having a nuclear weapon
OL,17,F` one of the key issues Washington
OL,18,Fsays is driving its war.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
