PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776359147
OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,F"We're going to make it economically
OL,7,Fprosperous, and we're going to invite
OL,8,Fthe Iranian people into the world
OL,9,Feconomy in a way they haven't been in
OL,10,Fmy entire life," he told a Turning
OL,11,FPoint USA event in Georgia.
OL,13,FVance added that Trump "doesn't want
OL,14,Fto make, like, a small deal. He wants
OL,15,Fto make the grand bargain".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
