OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,FPakistan said on Tuesday that it was
OL,7,Fpursuing efforts to help the US and
OL,8,FIran negotiate an end to the war,
OL,9,Fafter Trump told the New York Post
OL,10,Fearlier that a second round of talks
OL,11,Fwith Iran "could be happening over
OL,12,Fnext two days".
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Lebanese Ambassador to the
OL,15,FUS Nada Hamadeh Moawad said talks
OL,16,Fbetween Lebanon and Israel in
OL,17,FWashington were "constructive".
