OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,FThe war in Iran reignited fighting
OL,7,Fbetween Israel and Hezbollah militants
OL,8,Fin Lebanon, and Washington has said
OL,9,Fthis strand of the conflict is not
OL,10,Fincluded in the ongoing ceasefire.
OL,12,FIsraeli Ambassador to the US, Yechiel
OL,13,FLeiter praised his Lebanese
OL,14,Fcounterparts after the two-hour
OL,15,Fmeeting, saying "we're on the same
OL,16,Fside of the equation."
OL,18,FThe Lebanese militant group Hezbollah
OL,19,Fopposes the direct talks and has said
OL,20,Fit won't abide by any agreements made
OL,21,Fas a result.
