OL,3,CUS says blockade has completely halted
OL,4,Ctrade at Iran's ports
OL,6,FThe fighting in the Middle East has
OL,7,Fkilled at least 3,000 people in Iran,
OL,8,Fmore than 2,100 in Lebanon, 23 in
OL,9,FIsrael and more than a dozen in Gulf
OL,10,FArab states. In addition, 13 US
OL,11,Fservice members have been killed.
